{"tid":2511562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"信國安法！東張女神李旻芳擲692.5萬買西貢逸瓏，花園放狗","createTime":"2021-05-01T04:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T07:25:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0079c7b0fce6050b873bb73f1980c08bef9d6e15","tid":2511562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MG6QbpxzMeUiaYq3jOSlpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/CQ66SIWUKXDgnTtzYzyLjQ--~B/aD01NDA7dz01NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/thesun.hk.com/76a28d87f72a747a52d10dad2ad376ba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMG6QbpxzMeUiaYq3jOSlpg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCQ66SIWUKXDgnTtzYzyLjQ--~B%2FaD01NDA7dz01NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F76a28d87f72a747a52d10dad2ad376ba&h=ed555934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「東張女神」李旻芳以首置身份入市，以692.5萬購入西貢逸瓏海滙2座低層連花園單位，物業實用面積433方呎，連約235方呎花園。<br />\n<br />\n李旻芳的老公黃耀英接受電話訪問時，透露單位是自住，而且是樓換樓：「因為狗狗行動唔方便，呢度冇樓梯，加上有花園畀佢走動。另一個原因係太太體諒我，見我年紀大，唔想我行樓梯，哈哈！」提到業主是太太，他直言兩公婆不分你我：「我哋對錢銀觀念唔係睇得好重，落佢名唔係問題，一齊供啫！（預計幾時搬？）未有確實日子，買住先。」"},{"pid":"17db2345bfa495b9d2bc801b01dfd0c874e9fded","tid":2511562,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"冇大波圖 好似唔係幾夠"},{"pid":"e48a94dc79ad4ddb2f004ef27536f28f4ddcce30","tid":2511562,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17db2345bfa495b9d2bc801b01dfd0c874e9fded","tid":2511562,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"冇大波圖 好似唔係幾夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"PUSH UP BRA 啫"},{"pid":"1716bbdf3fc635410fd11a04fec89a4bc20e1df6","tid":2511562,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci